      <lom xsi:schemaLocation="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/lomv1.0/lomLoose.xsd" xmlns="http://ltsc.ieee.org/xsd/LOM">

          <title>
            <string language="en">Tally of the 1824 Electoral College Vote</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Tally der Wahlmänner-Gremium 1824 Stimme</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Comptage de la voix de l'université 1824 
électorale</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Registro do voto da faculdade 1824 electoral</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Riscontro del voto dell'università elettorale 
1824</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Έλεγχος της εκλογικής ψηφοφορίας κολλεγίου 1824</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Cuenta del voto de la universidad electoral 1824</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">focuses on the complex system of election rules by examining the vote tally of the 1824 Presidential election, in which the winning candidate, John Quincy Adams, received fewer popular votes than the runner-up, Andrew Jackson.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Social Sciences</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Foki auf dem komplexen System der Wahlrichtlinien 
durch das Überprüfen des Stimmetallys der Präsidentenwahl 1824, in 
der der gewinnende Anwärter, John Quincy Adams, wenige populäre 
Stimmen als der Zweite empfing, Andrew Jackson.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">foyers sur le système complexe des règles 
d'élection en examinant le comptage de voix de l'élection 1824 
présidentielle, dans laquelle le candidat de gain, John Quincy Adams,
a reçu moins de voix populaires que le runner-up, Andrew Jackson.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">focos no sistema complexo de réguas da eleição 
examinando o registro do voto da eleição 1824 presidencial, em que o
candidato ganhando, John Quincy Adams, recebeu poucos votos populares 
do que o runner-up, Andrew Jackson.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">fuochi sul sistema complesso delle regole di 
elezione esaminando il riscontro di voto dell'elezione presidenziale 
1824, in cui il candidato di vincita, John Quincy Adams, ha ricevuto 
pochi voti popolari che il runner-up, Andrew Jackson.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">εστίαση στο σύνθετο σύστημα των κανόνων εκλογής με 
την εξέταση του ελέγχου ψηφοφορίας της προεδρικής εκλογής 
1824, στην οποία ο κερδίζοντας υποψήφιος, John Quincy 
Adams, έλαβε λιγότερες δημοφιλείς ψηφοφορίες από 
δρομέας-επάνω, Andrew Τζάκσον.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">focos en el sistema complejo de las reglas de la 
elección examinando la cuenta del voto de la elección presidencial 
1824, en la cual el candidato que ganaba, Juan Quincy Adams, recibió 
pocos votos populares que el runner-up, Andrew Jackson.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Sozialwissenschaften</string>
          </keyword>
